column5: Hello all,We go up fishing in Canada every year. Every year we have a little saying or theme for our vaction. This year we haven't been able to come up with one. Our first one was "Refusa to losa". We have had various ones since then but are now drawing a blank. We were wondering if you could help us out and give us some suggestions. Thank you for your timeK-man
"Go Hard or Go Home"Worked for us for many years....derrek.CANADIAN WALLEYE OPEN UP AND SAY "EH"!
"Who Farted?"Stay off the pipe...and don't forget to wipe.Red
for reply #3 shouldn't that be hoof hearted ??, for a slogan....do the Blue
We had a guy in the boat that we thought was a "smart feller", but he turned out to be just a . . .
